      <title>巴拿马运河需要今年剩余时间才能从干旱中恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/panama-canal-will-need-rest-of-year-to-recover-from-drought</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拿马运河至少需要今年剩余时间才能从 2023 年的干旱中完全恢复，这场干旱导致水位下降、船舶交通堵塞，并使托运人损失了数百万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/panama-canal-will-need-rest-of-year-to-recover-from-drought</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:27:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
